OL,4,CPROGRAMMES
OL,5,
OL,6,CG2023FDuring ITV's coverage of King
OL,7,FCharles III's coronation, actress Adjoa
OL,8,FAndoh commented that the balcony of
OL,9,FBuckingham Palace looked "terribly
OL,10,Fwhite".
OL,11,
OL,12,FOfcom received 8,421 complaints about
OL,13,Fthe comment - the 10th-highest figure
OL,14,Fsince 2004.
OL,15,
OL,16,FThe comment was assessed but not
OL,17,Fpursued.
